ActOther Than Statutory Authority
SubjectAppointment of the Surveyor General of Canada
PrecisAppointment of the Surveyor General of Canada ex officio as a member of each of the following boundary commissions: (a) British Columbia-Yukon-Northwest Territories; (b) Saskatchewan-Northwest Territories; (c) Manitoba-Saskatchewan; and (d) Alberta-Northwest Territories.
